location.fullValue: Kaufman Plan, Aldervista at North Ranch

data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 4 bedroom, 3 bath home! The kitchen creates a spacious and inviting atmosphere, perfect for family gatherings and entertaining guests. Enjoy the views of the park across the street, bringing nature right to your doorstep. This lovely house features shutters and faux wood flooring which adds a touch of warmth and charm to the common areas. With a split entry design, this home offers convenience and functionality with a 2 car garage for ample storage space for vehicles. Additionally, its close proximity to Nellis Airforce Base, VA Hospital, and freeways ensures easy access to amenities and transportation. You'll also find yourself just a short distance away from a variety of restaurants and grocery stores, making daily errands a breeze. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own this home!
